WEBVTT

00:11.080 --> 00:12.115
-Hey.
-Hey.

00:12.280 --> 00:15.670
Big news. The dog problem
has been solved.

00:15.840 --> 00:16.829
Really? What happened?

00:17.000 --> 00:18.911
Well, there's this rabbi
in my building--

00:19.080 --> 00:20.957
You've met him.
He's a very nice man.

00:21.120 --> 00:23.998
-ls he the one with the show on cable?
-Yeah, yeah, that's the one.

00:24.160 --> 00:27.391
So I spoke to him about the dog,
he went down, talked to the owner...

00:27.560 --> 00:30.028
...and she agreed to keep the dog
inside from now on.

00:30.200 --> 00:32.634
-That's great.
-I know.

